						.col-md-6.col-lg-12
							+box-icon-modern({
								classMod: 'decorate-circle',
								icon: 'linearicons-hamburger icon-gradient-2',
								title: 'Tasty Food'
							})
								p At Eventy, you can find a wide range of tasty food and beverages.
						.col-md-6.col-lg-12
							+box-icon-modern({
								classMod: 'decorate-rectangle',
								icon: 'linearicons-music-note2 icon-gradient-4',
								title: 'Live Music'
							})
								p One of the main reasons to visit Eventy is great live music and performances.
								
